snippet.title: Capybara Quest Trailer
snippet.description:
Official trailer for my new homebrew Gameboy Color game; Capybara Quest!

Available completely free to play either in-browser, on mobile, or downloaded for emulator or real hardware use: https://maxthetics.itch.io/capybara-quest
